---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start">
    
    <div class="md:col-span-4 space-y-8">
      <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg border-4 border-white aspect-square bg-slate-100">
        <img src="/img/ledoug.jpg" alt="Christoph Kittel" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition duration-500" />
      </div>

      <section class="space-y-4">
        <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold border-b border-slate-200 pb-2 text-slate-900">Contact</h3>
        
        <div class="text-sm space-y-5">
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-blue-950 mb-1.5 uppercase tracking-tight text-xs">University of Liège</p>
            <p>Laboratory of Climatology (SPHERES)</p>
            <p>Office B11, Clos Mercator 3</p>
            <p>4000 Liège, Belgium</p>
            <a href="mailto:ckittel@uliege.be" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline">ckittel@uliege.be</a>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-blue-950 mb-1.5 uppercase tracking-tight text-xs">Vrije Universiteit Brussel</p>
            <p>Assistant Professor (Climate Modelling)</p>
            <p>Department of Geography</p>
            <p>Room F4.65, Pleinlaan 2</p>
            <p>1050 Brussels, Belgium</p>
            <a href="mailto:christoph.kittel@vub.be" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline">christoph.kittel@vub.be</a>
          </div>

          <div class="pt-4 border-t border-slate-100 space-y-3">
            <a href="https://orcid.org/0000-0002-3112-8704" target="_blank" class="flex items-center group transition" title="View ORCID Profile">
              <img src="https://orcid.org/sites/default/files/images/orcid_16x16.png" class="w-4 h-4 flex-none" alt="ORCID" />
              <span class="text-slate-500 group-hover:text-blue-700 text-xs ml-3 font-medium transition-colors">ORCID Profile</span>
            </a>

            <a href="https://www.uliege.be/cms/c_9054334/fr/repertoire?uid=U223159" target="_blank" class="flex items-center group transition" title="ULiège Directory">
              <img src="/img/uliege_logo.png" class="w-4 h-4 flex-none object-contain" alt="ULiège" />
              <span class="text-slate-500 group-hover:text-blue-700 text-xs ml-3 font-medium transition-colors">ULiège Directory</span>
            </a>

            <a href="https://fard.research.vub.be/christoph-kittel" target="_blank" class="flex items-center group transition" title="VUB Research Portal">
              <img src="/imglogos/vub°logo.png" class="w-4 h-4 flex-none object-contain" alt="VUB" />
              <span class="text-slate-500 group-hover:text-orange-700 text-xs ml-3 font-medium transition-colors">VUB Research Portal</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="md:col-span-8 space-y-12">
      <header>
        <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-950 mb-3 tracking-tighter">Christoph Kittel</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-blue-900 font-medium tracking-tight">FNRS Postdoctoral Researcher (ULiège) & Assistant Professor (VUB)</p>
      </header>

      <section class="prose prose-slate lg:prose-lg max-w-none text-slate-800 text-justify leading-relaxed space-y-6">
        <p>
          I am an FNRS Postdoctoral Researcher at the University of Liège (ULiège) and an Assistant Professor in Climate Modelling at the Vrije Universiteit Brussel (VUB). I hold a Master’s degree in Geography (specializing in Climatology) and a PhD in Climatology from ULiège.
        </p>
        <p>
          My research is dedicated to understanding the role of ice sheets within the polar climate system, particularly in the face of current climate change. I investigate complex interactions between ice dynamics, the atmosphere, and the ocean using coupled polar climate models. Furthermore, I am developing the integration of AI methods into these models to better account for these interactions in long-term climate projections and reduce associated uncertainties.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100">
        <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center text-slate-900">
          <span class="w-8 h-px bg-blue-600 mr-4"></span> Research Interests
        </h3>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          {[
            'Ice Sheet Dynamics', 'Polar Climate Modeling', 'Atmosphere-Ocean Interaction', 
            'Climate Projections', 'Sea Level Rise', 'AI in Geosciences'
          ].map((tag) => (
            <span class="px-4 py-1.5 bg-slate-50 text-slate-600 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full border border-slate-200 hover:border-blue-300 hover:text-blue-700 transition-all cursor-default">
              {tag}
            </span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>
      
      <section class="space-y-6">
         <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold border-b border-slate-100 pb-2 text-slate-900">Positions</h3>
         <div class="relative pl-8 border-l-2 border-slate-200 space-y-8">

              <div class="relative">
              <div class="absolute -left-[37px] top-1 w-4 h-4 bg-slate-600 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-sm"></div>
              <p class="font-bold text-slate-950 leading-tight">FNRS Postdoctoral Researcher</p>
              <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-600 font-black uppercase tracking-wider">Since 2024 · University of Liège (ULiège)</p>
            </div>

            <div class="relative">
              <div class="absolute -left-[37px] top-1 w-4 h-4 bg-blue-500 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-sm"></div>
              <p class="font-bold text-slate-950 leading-tight">Assistant Professor (Climate Modelling)</p>
              <p class="text-[10px] text-blue-600 font-black uppercase tracking-wider">Since 2024 · Vrije Universiteit Brussel (VUB)</p>
            </div>


            
            <div class="relative">
              <div class="absolute -left-[37px] top-1 w-4 h-4 bg-slate-300 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-sm"></div>
              <p class="font-bold text-slate-950 leading-tight">Postdoctoral Researcher</p>
              <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-black uppercase tracking-wider">2022 – 2024 · IGE, Université Grenoble Alpes (France)</p>
            </div>

            <div class="relative">
              <div class="absolute -left-[37px] top-1 w-4 h-4 bg-slate-200 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-sm"></div>
              <p class="font-bold text-slate-950 leading-tight">Postdoctoral Researcher</p>
              <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-black uppercase tracking-wider">2021 – 2021 · University of Liège (ULiège)</p>
            </div>

            <div class="relative">
              <div class="absolute -left-[37px] top-1 w-4 h-4 bg-slate-100 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-sm"></div>
              <p class="font-bold text-slate-950 leading-tight">PhD Candidate / Research Scientist</p>
              <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-black uppercase tracking-wider">2016 – 2021 · University of Liège (ULiège)</p>
            </div>
         </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>